{"tid":1554762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【遊戲攻略】分化敵國前線方法，令一眾士兵懷疑人生","createTime":"2019-09-09T05:58:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T06:04:29.000Z","uid":280136,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"890f907a8ad49e3871c801aee6ea15033e77df88","tid":1554762,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T05:58:36.000Z","msg":"玩過三國志嘅朋友都知道，只要你係咁<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">離間</span></span>武將同主公，好快武將就會對主公失去信心，士氣低落甚至棄甲曳兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而前線嘅士兵，承受嘅壓力係最大，一方面三過家門不入，未知嬌妻有冇勾佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二黎一旦情緒低落，士氣低下，作戰力就會下降甚至做<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">25仔</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化主公同武將</span></span>係非常之重要嘅，正如孫子兵法有云：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攻心為上</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（古語有云 一直係用E個云，唔係殘體字黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n一旦前線士兵覺得後方有機會出賣自己，士氣仲唔跌到撲街？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我地可以係每一局遊戲都嘗試用新嘅兵種、新嘅方法去攻心，場game豈不是好快就贏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc2740c80c4edfc5657e77e4febed829db44a3b","tid":1554762,"uid":280136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"p牌冇得推，有冇大佬可以幫幫拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}